I added a new test file `snapshot_retention_test.go` that validates the fix by:
1. Creating multiple snapshots over time
2. Verifying that `rootBoltSnapshotMetaData()` returns recent snapshots (within expiration duration)
3. Ensuring old snapshots are not included in the results

The fix ensures that snapshot cleanup and retention policies work correctly, preventing loss of recent snapshots and proper cleanup of old ones.

